title: Ep - 11 - The Bachelor's Catherine Giudici,  Teen Mom OG & Marriage Bootcamp
description:
Kate interviews Catherine Giudici Lowe from The Bachelor, chats with actor and writer Bill Savage about Martha Stewart and Snoop Dog's new cooking show, her old roommate Maura about Teen Mom OG, and her friend Ashley about Marriage Bootcamp: Reality Stars.
